  "texts": [
    "In this experiment, we pruned 8 fixed middle layers, from the 12th to the 19th layer, inclusively.",
    "After fine-tuning both models with the Englishto-German ACL 60/60 dataset, the model where only the decoder layers were pruned achieved 4+ additional points in terms of BLEU and chrF++ and 18+ points of COMET.",
    "It is worth noting that both the number of parameters and the storage footprint of this model is only 1% larger than the model with both the encoder and decoder were pruned.",
